# Card Highlight debug

- **`/debug`** on the deployed site loads (200); the embedded API calls return **404** `{ error: "Not found" }` until **`ENABLE_DEBUG_CARDTRADER=1`** is set on Vercel (then JSON payloads appear).
- User can run **`npm run debug:card`** (with `npm run dev` on `localhost:3000`, or `SITE_URL=https://… npm run debug:card` for production if `ENABLE_DEBUG_CARDTRADER=1`).
- That writes **`last-card-debug.json`** at repo root (gitignored) and prints the same JSON to stdout.
- When the user asks what the card debug says or to interpret it, **read `last-card-debug.json`** if it exists; otherwise ask them to run `npm run debug:card` or open `/debug` and retry.
